bill.summary: 8/3/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1995, the duty on: (1) diphenylguanidine and di-o-tolylguanidine; and (2) dicyclohexylbenzothiazylsulfenamide.
